node.text:
It’s all about the design, isn’t it? ✨
@haljashouses has brought into existence a product beyond the boundaries of design.
A product dependent on it’s environment.

‘Hele’ is an octagon-shaped sauna that offers a sociable experience for up to 7 people. The double-glazed mirrorglass offers privacy while the visitors can still enjoy a 360 degree view.

🔸 For more visit www.Haljas.com
